    <item>
      <title>随着股票反弹，印度尼西亚延迟了卖空实施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/indonesian-regulator-holds-meeting-to-discuss-market-conditions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的金融监管机构将推迟投资者短暂销售股票，因为上周陷入熊市后，美国的主要股票量规弹回来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/indonesian-regulator-holds-meeting-to-discuss-market-conditions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:23:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着特朗普的仇恨动摇东欧交易，乌克兰的债券下降了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自去年重组以来，乌克兰的美元债券是美国和欧洲对和平进程之间的分裂以来最多的，这使投资者期望有序地朝着停火前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ukraine-bonds-drop-as-trump-feud-shakes-up-east-european-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 09:13:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲国防股票以军事支出承诺跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/european-defense-stocks-jump-as-leaders-show-support-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该地区政治领导人向乌克兰提供支持之后，欧洲国防股飙升，占地约300亿美元，并承诺在美国回落的担忧中提高国防支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/european-defense-stocks-jump-as-leaders-show-support-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 07:09:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度高等法院聆听监管机构在调查前的上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/india-court-orders-corruption-probe-of-ex-market-regulator-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度法院已同意听取该国的证券监管机构和证券交易所经营者的上诉，以审查另一个法院对官员处理股份发行的命令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/india-court-orders-corruption-probe-of-ex-market-regulator-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 05:01:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行率削减进入最终拉伸，分区正在扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ecb-interest-rate-cuts-enter-final-stretch-with-divisions-widening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲中央银行接近其利率削减周期的最后一站，内部部门将在未来几个月内使决策复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/ecb-interest-rate-cuts-enter-final-stretch-with-divisions-widening</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
